{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9d10585c87","title":"毛泽东关于办好省报问题给刘建勋、韦国清的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"59cc1054f6","index":0,"year":1958,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"9d10585c87"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3ae36abefb","name":"刘建勋","type":"人物"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"05fdb62d42","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于办好省报问题给刘建勋、韦国清的信","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"58e1e78b51","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"6422d12a00","type":"appellation","text":"刘建勋、韦国清二同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"780d81d928","type":"paragraph","text":"送上几份地方报纸，各有特点，是比较编得好的，较为引人看，内容也不错，供你们参考。省报问题是一个极重要问题，值得认真研究，同广西日报的编辑们一道，包括版面、新闻、社论、理论、文艺等项。钻进去，想了又想，分析又分析，同各省报纸比较又比较，几个月时间就可以找出一条道路来的。精心写作社论是一项极重要任务，你们自己、宣传部长、秘书长、报社总编辑，要共同研究。第一书记挂帅，动手修改一些最重要的社论，是必要的。一张省报，对于全省工作，全体人民，有极大的组织、鼓舞、激励、批判、推动的作用。请你们想一想这个问题，以为如何?","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"c6c55b49f3","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东一九五八年一月十二日上午七时","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"df6fa3f025","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"480ef4fa9e","type":"appellation","text":"即送乔木同志：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"05a76004c1","type":"paragraph","text":"可以在新闻界的刊物上发表。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9d10585c87"},{"id":"04